YUMI 2.0.5.8 + Portable - Your Universal Multiboot Installer

YUMI (Your Universal Multiboot Installer)&#xA0;is a small handy tool with which you can easily create a multiboot USB disk containing for example several operating systems, various anti-virus tools for cleaning your PC from viruses (AVG Rescue CD,

Acronis Rescue CD, AVIRA AntiVir Rescue CD, BitDefender Rescue Disk, Dr.Web Live CD, Panda SafeCD, Kaspersky Rescue Disk), system utilities (CloneZilla, EASUS Disk Copy, FreeDOS, GParted, Memtest86 +, Parted Magic, Ultimate Boot CD), etc.

There is an option to specify an ISO image, located on the hard disk, or download the required software from the official site.

YUMI (Your Universal Multiboot Installer),&#xA0;is the successor to MultibootISOs.&#xA0;It can be used to create a Multiboot USB Flash Drive containing multiple operating systems, antivirus utilities, disc cloning, diagnostic tools, and more.

Contrary to MultiBootISO&apos;s which used grub to boot ISO files directly from USB, YUMI uses syslinux to boot.

Distributions can also be uninstalled using the same tool!&#xA0;YUMI is freeware.&#xA0;However, if you enjoy using YUMI and would like to help support its development, please consider making a donation.

